        of law in <ja_class>NXOpen.GeometricUtilities.LawBuilder</ja_class>.
        Objects of class <ja_class>NXOpen.GeometricUtilities.TransitionLawNodeBuilder</ja_class> are used
        as law nodes in <ja_class>NXOpen.GeometricUtilities.MultiTransitionLawBuilder</ja_class>. Spine
